	9/26/1994--Introduced.
Energy Policy and Conservation Act Amendments of 1994 - Amends the Energy Policy and Conservation Act to extend from September 30, 1994, to June 30, 1996: (1) the President's authority relating to domestic energy supply availability; and (2) the President's standby energy authorities.

